      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"8. LEXINGTON QUEEN has been close up in both starts since a spell, coming from a similar barrier to this for second when resuming at Ashburton before a fourth last start at Ruakaka. Building in fitness so could break through. 3. JESSIE LINCOLN only beat one home when resuming at Alexandra Park but should find this easier. Draws well so can measure up in this line-up. 4. AWESOME WISH is a three-year-old gelding by Lazarus on debut. Has hinted at ability at the trials so is worth keeping safe. 13. LINCOLN DEALER is another that faces the starter for the first time. By American Ideal and hails from the Ray Green & Nathan Delany stable. May feature with luck from the draw.\",\"runners\":[8,3,4,13],\"exclusive\":false}",
